race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X Grade 5 Series H Pr1 Div
race.comment: HUNTSMAN (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (22.98) at Gawler. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Good form should continue. NOLA KEEPING (2) was never in contention last time at Angle Park, but prior to that won by 1.75 lengths at Gawler (31.15) beating Boom Boom Jack in a Grade 5 on October 26. Hard to knock her form from this box, unbeaten in three starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. PRIME VOLTAGE (7) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.
